## ğŸ“Š Performance

We compared three model scales on the BIS dataset. The **Small (s)** variant offers the best trade-off between speed and accuracy.

| Model Variant | Parameters | mAP@50 | Inference Speed |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **YOLOv8n-Seg** (Nano) | 3.2M | 0.628 | âš¡ Very Fast |
| **YOLOv8s-Seg** (Small) | 11.2M | **0.651** | âš–ï¸ **Balanced** |
| **YOLOv8m-Seg** (Medium) | 25.9M | 0.613 | ğŸ¢ Slower |

